      • setRegion

        private void setRegion()
        This method sets the region of the current user to use for local rankings. It first checks for permissions and requests it. If permission is not granted, the default location is used

      • updateRegion

        public void updateRegion()
        This method gets the user's postal code from their current location and update this value in the database. If the postal code cannot be determined, the last known region in the database is used
